title: QUEENS TO PROMOTE THEIR TOWNSHIPS AT MISS FIJI PAGEANT (Government of the Republic of Fiji) ...
text: ( Source : Government of the Republic of Fiji ) 10/8/ 2015 Fijians for the first time will witness the 2015 Miss Fiji Pageant in Nadi later this month whereby 10 winning queens from various townships will contest at a national level. Minister
